item.title: CVE-2023-46231|2024-09-30T17:57:23.306Z -- splunk -- splunk%20add-on%20builder
item.description: In Splunk Add-on Builder versions below 4.1.4, the application writes user session tokens to its internal log files when you visit the Splunk Add-on Builder or when you build or edit a custom app or add-on.
